Details for creating Event :
→ event name
→ location (include ground, seminar hall....)
→ description (info about event)
→ type(cultural, educational, sports ....) and subType
→ date and Timings(for knowing if location is available or not)
→ price(optional for paid events)
→ department( eg  chemical, electrical,..)
→ organiser contact details (name, department, email,...)